<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 01:50:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>利用月球风化层建造月球栖息地</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/using-moon-regolith-to-build-lunar-habitats</link><description>“我们的结果表明，您可以将一种本质上具有挑战性的材料转化为对结构有益的材料，”Denizhan Yavas 博士说。 [&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/using-moon-regolith-to-build-lunar-habitats.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 01:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/using-moon-regolith-to-build-lunar-habitats</guid></item><item><title>领悟经验：洞见与神秘经验的融合</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/realization-experiences-a-convergent-account-of-insight-and-mystical-experiences</link><description>我们认为，神秘型体验的强大变革效应可以使用洞察力解决问题的相同机制来理解，神秘体验和洞察力都是“实现体验”的一个种类：某些现象或信息突然被体验为真实或真实的体验。具体来说，我们认为，以这种方式理解这两种方式使我们能够通过行为熵和图论的相同组合来建模神秘体验，这些组合已成功用于建模洞察问题解决。从新信息和先前表征之间的紧张关系开始，代理破坏其表征网络的稳定性，使其进入显着性改变和关联增强的状态以更新网络。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/realization-experiences-a-convergent-account-of-insight-and-mystical-experiences2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 01:35:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/realization-experiences-a-convergent-account-of-insight-and-mystical-experiences</guid></item><item><title>下一个芯片突破不是机器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-next-chip-breakthrough-is-not-a-machine</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 01:20:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-next-chip-breakthrough-is-not-a-machine</guid></item><item><title>这些比头发小 50 倍的微型机器人可以捕猎和移动细菌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/these-tiny-robots-50x-smaller-than-a-hair-can-hunt-and-move-bacteria</link><description>光子驱动的纳米机器人可以精确地引导、捕获和移动细菌，从而能够在微观环境中进行受控操作，并为微生物学提供新工具。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/these-tiny-robots-50x-smaller-than-a-hair-can-hunt-and-move-bacteria.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 01:05:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/these-tiny-robots-50x-smaller-than-a-hair-can-hunt-and-move-bacteria</guid></item><item><title>科学家发现如何冷冻移植器官而不破裂它们</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-discover-how-to-freeze-transplant-organs-without-cracking-them</link><description>科学家们正在朝着冷冻器官以供将来使用而不损坏它们的方向迈出一大步。一项新的研究表明，最大的障碍之一——超冷保存过程中的开裂——可以通过仔细调节组织进入玻璃态的温度来减少。这一突破建立在最近在低温保存器官移植方面取得的成功的基础上，可以使长期以来想象的“储存”器官以供以后使用的想法更接近现实。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-discover-how-to-freeze-transplant-organs-without-cracking-them.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 00:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-discover-how-to-freeze-transplant-organs-without-cracking-them</guid></item><item><title>细菌防御系统以意想不到的新方式构建 DNA 来阻止病毒</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/bacterial-defense-system-builds-dna-in-unexpected-new-way-to-stop-viruses</link><description>斯坦福大学的科学家发现，细菌中发现的一种独特的防御系统 DRT3 可以产生 DNA 来抵御病毒感染。 DRT3 由两种不同的酶（称为逆转录酶）Drt3a 和 Drt3b 以及一段非编码 RNA (ncRNA) 组成。这三者共同构成了由交替重复序列 (GT/AC) 组成的长双链 DNA。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/bacterial-defense-system-builds-dna-in-unexpected-new-way-to-stop-viruses2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 00:35:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/bacterial-defense-system-builds-dna-in-unexpected-new-way-to-stop-viruses</guid></item><item><title>卵泡抑素和肌肉质量：重新思考基线</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/follistatin-muscle-mass-rethinking-the-baseline</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 00:20:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/follistatin-muscle-mass-rethinking-the-baseline</guid></item><item><title>物理学家揭示时间旅行如何成为可能 |吉姆·哈利利</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/a-physicist-reveals-how-time-travel-is-possible-jim-al-khalili</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 00:05:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/a-physicist-reveals-how-time-travel-is-possible-jim-al-khalili</guid></item><item><title>中国阻止 Meta 以 20 亿美元收购人工智能集团 Manus</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/china-blocks-metas-2bn-purchase-of-ai-group-manus</link><description>监管机构已审查该交易是否违反北京的投资规定&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/china-blocks-metas-2bn-purchase-of-ai-group-manus2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 23:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/china-blocks-metas-2bn-purchase-of-ai-group-manus</guid></item><item><title>为什么是一门学科：古德哈特定律和人工智能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-why-is-a-discipline-goodharts-law-and-ai</link><description>本周一位读者问了我一个问题，从那时起我就一直在思考这个问题。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-why-is-a-discipline-goodharts-law-and-ai2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 23:35:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-why-is-a-discipline-goodharts-law-and-ai</guid></item></channel></rss>